getByRole (Most Recommended ⭐)
await page.getByRole('button', { name: 'Login' }).click();

Important (VERY IMPORTANT for interview)
👉 getByTestId() works ONLY if:
Attribute exists:
data-testid="value"
await page.getByTestId('username'); // data-testid="username"

2. 📝 getByText
await page.getByText('Login').click();
3. 🏷️ getByLabel

👉 Forms ke liye best

await page.getByLabel('Username').fill('test');
await page.getByLabel('Password').fill('1234');
4. 🧪 getByPlaceholder
await page.getByPlaceholder('Username').fill('test');

✔ Jab label nahi ho
5. 🧾 getByTestId (SUPER IMPORTANT 🔥)

👉 Dev team se bolna:

<button data-testid="login-btn">Login</button>
await page.getByTestId('login-btn').click();

6. 🎯 CSS Locator
await page.locator('#username').fill('test');
await page.locator('.btn-primary').click();
7. 🧬 XPath (Avoid if possible)
await page.locator('//input[@id="username"]').fill('test');

❌ Last option

8. Chaining (Playwright Power 💥)
await page.locator('form').getByRole('button', { name: 'Login' }).click();
Parent → child relation
9. Filtering (Advanced 🔥)
await page.getByRole('button').filter({ hasText: 'Login' }).click();

10. Multiple Elements Handle
const items = page.locator('.inventory_item');

Best Locator Priority (Interview Answer)

